Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:23:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fanculo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhanh lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta sẽ không đầu hàng!
